imdb.plot outline: Mónica Fonseca, Colombian hostess, will help you create your own style and make yours the most edgy and newest trends before they become popular. Fashion, health, beauty, eco, tech, design and travel trends will get to you first, and you'll be able to know who are the creative people and forces behind them. Thus, you will stand out in the crowd!
